_sText: FY BUZZKILL ICEAGE So herm, I completly forgot about the Time Traveller Contest, and basicly started it a few hours ago. NO, I'm not proud of it, but atleast I managed to finish it. Was quite challenging. The concenpt is quite simple, make it look more futuristic, keeping the gameplay as classy as possible. You'll also notice (if you play test it) some influences I got from other classic maps such as Ice World and Pool Party. DONE.DONE.DONE. Meh, have fun I guess.
